"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-20-Chinese-weightlifter-Liu-Huanhua-eyes-gold-at-Paris-Olympics-1uAzONfyk80-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  In the world of weightlifting, the 100 kg plus category has always been a challenge for China, with a gold medal lacking from the country's Olympic haul.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9914779612217253, \"rank\": 0.008157658109100425, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Liu Huanhua, set to make his Games debut in Paris, is determined to change that narrative.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997802426847, \"rank\": 2.1975729836245355e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old's journey to the Olympics has been nothing short of extraordinary.\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His triumph at last year's World Weightlifting Championships saw him clinch two gold medals in the 102 kg category, ending a 26-year-long drought for China's men's weightlifting team in that category.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9914779612217253, \"rank\": 0.008157658109100425, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite moving up to the 109 kg category at the Hangzhou Asian Games last year, he continued to dominate.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Weightlifting World Cup earlier this year, Liu shattered two world records in the 102 kg category.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Paris Olympics loom closer, Liu says his rigorous training and good form have him brimming with confidence.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As an athlete, it's crucial to dare to compete on the battlefield.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But at the end of the day, solid pre-match training is key.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's only through rigorous training that you build the foundation to compete.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will be amazed at the energy you discover within yourself, which greatly boosts your self-confidence,\\\" said Liu.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": []}]}"